    <text>
        <body>
            <div type="transcript" id="P90-79">
                <lg type="stanza">
                    <l>Safe in their alabaster chambers,</l>
                    <l>Untouched by morning and untouched by noon,</l>
                    <l>Sleep the meek members of the resurrection,</l>
                    <l>Rafter of satin, and roof of stone.</l>
                </lg>
                <lg type="stanza">
                    <l>Light laughs the breeze in her castle of sunshine;</l>
                    <l>Babbles the bee in a stolid ear;</l>
                    <l>Pipe the sweet birds in ignorant cadence, </l>
                    <l>Ah, what sagacity perished here!</l>
                </lg>
                <lg type="stanza">
                    <l>Grand go the years in the crescent above them;</l>
                    <l>Worlds scoop their arcs, and firmaments row,</l>
                    <l>Diadems drop and Doges surrender,</l>
                    <l>Soundless as dots on a disk of snow.</l>
                </lg>

            </div>     
